goals.active: Rescue Demmi Beetlestone from the Jackdaw pirates.
goals.complete: We rescued Demmi and got her safely back to Lion's Arch. She'll be waiting for me at the safehouse there.

goals.active: Locate the Order of Whispers safehouse in Lion's Arch.
goals.complete: I talked with the bouncer inside the tavern in Lion's Arch. With the proper passwords, I was allowed into the secret Order of Whispers hideout.

goals.active: I should make sure Tybalt and Demmi made it to the safehouse.
goals.complete: Tybalt and Demmi arrived safely in Lion's Arch, but they were tracked via her enchanted necklace and she had to be snuck out of the city again.
